## Third-Party Services

### Apple Services
TradeFrame integrates with CloudKit (iCloud sync), App Store/StoreKit (subscriptions), EventKit (calendar), Speech Framework (voice-to-text), and Core Location (GPS). All governed by Apple's privacy policies.

### Google AdMob
Used for serving banner advertisements to free-tier users only. See "Advertising" section above.

