## Data Sharing

### We Do Not Sell Your Data
We do not sell, rent, trade, or share your personal data with any third party.

### You Control Sharing
Data only leaves your device through: (1) iCloud sync to your personal account, (2) PDFs you share via the iOS share sheet, (3) CSV exports you initiate, or (4) advertising data collected by AdMob for free-tier users (see Advertising section). In cases 1-3, you control the sharing.

