- **Camera** — Required for photo documentation features
- **Location** — Optional — GPS-stamps photos with coordinates
- **Microphone** — Optional — enables voice note transcription
- **Calendar** — Optional — syncs job dates to Apple Calendar
- **Notifications** — Optional — job reminders, invoice nudges, payment alerts
