## Data Retention & Deletion

### Your Data, Your Control
Data remains on your device and in your iCloud account for as long as you use the app. We cannot delete your data remotely because we do not store it.

### How to Delete
Delete individual records within the app. Uninstall TradeFrame to remove all local data. For iCloud data, go to iOS Settings → [Your Name] → iCloud → Manage Storage → TradeFrame.

---

## Subscriptions & Payments

Apple handles all payment processing through the App Store via StoreKit. We do not collect, process, or store any payment information. Manage or cancel subscriptions in iOS Settings → [Your Name] → Subscriptions.

---

## Security

- **Device Encryption** — iOS encrypts all app data when your device is locked (Data Protection)
- **iCloud Encryption** — Data synced via CloudKit is encrypted in transit and at rest by Apple
- **No Remote Access** — We do not operate servers that store or access your data

